---
title: Carb Smart Double Chicken in Onion Gravy with Roasted Veggies
description: Rich and unctuous onion gravy smothered all over chicken and roasted veggies is gorgeous enough to serve to as a Sunday feast! Lucky for you, you can have it on an ordinary weeknight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-double-dans-une-sauce-a-loignon-42045021.jpg
